function
Class FunctionEvaluator

java.lang.Object
  function.FunctionEvaluator
Direct Known Subclasses:
TabularFunction
public abstract class FunctionEvaluator
extends java.lang.Object

Function evaluator for MaxSum. This is an abstract class that gives the implementation of evaluateMod. Other methods must be implemented.

Author:
Michele Roncalli < roncallim at gmail dot com >
